Bai Ji.

203
00:11:57,610 --> 00:11:59,010
When you were
in your second year of high school,

204
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,320
there was a plague outbreak

205
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,440
in the townships of Quduo and Zuona.

206
00:12:05,030 --> 00:12:06,980
I was always leading medical teams

207
00:12:07,100 --> 00:12:08,150
to there back then.

208
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,100
Sometimes I didn't come home

209
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:12,140
for up to two months.

210
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:13,830
It was two months and 20 days.

211
00:12:19,250 --> 00:12:19,750
You told me

212
00:12:19,770 --> 00:12:21,020
