215
00:12:28,890 --> 00:12:29,870
Thinking back,

216
00:12:29,890 --> 00:12:31,160
that is the thing

217
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:34,340
I regret the most.

218
00:12:36,940 --> 00:12:37,480
Mom.

219
00:12:38,560 --> 00:12:39,150
I...

220
00:12:43,030 --> 00:12:44,620
