260
00:14:30,270 --> 00:14:31,390
Can you still move your hand?

261
00:14:32,660 --> 00:14:33,050
Yes.

262
00:14:33,680 --> 00:14:34,180
Go.

263
00:14:35,750 --> 00:14:37,040
Go help your eldest sister cook.

264
00:15:02,050 --> 00:15:02,750
What's wrong?

265
00:15:03,510 --> 00:15:04,700
If you have something to say, say it.

266
00:15:11,670 --> 00:15:13,300
I told Duojie today

267
00:15:13,400 --> 00:15:14,310
that I want to enter the mountains.

268
00:15:16,510 --> 00:15:17,330
He told me to come and ask

269
00:15:17,350 --> 00:15:18,160
for your opinion.

270
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:24,970
Say something, Mom.

271
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:28,620
What do you want me to say?

272
00:15:29,790 --> 00:15:31,200
That I agree to let you go?

273
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:35,370
Did you tell Duojie

274
00:15:35,390 --> 00:15:36,410
not to let me go?

275
00:15:44,370 --> 00:15:45,760
I used to think

276
00:15:46,520 --> 00:15:48,180
Duojie was giving me special treatment.

277
00:15:49,530 --> 00:15:50,960
I even complained to you about it.

278
00:15:52,050 --> 00:15:52,480
It turns out

279
00:15:52,510 --> 00:15:53,440
you were sabotaging me behind my back.

280
00:15:53,460 --> 00:15:54,700
How can you call that sabotage?

281
00:15:54,730 --> 00:15:56,200
If it's not sabotage, what is it?

282
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:57,980
What mother doesn't want

283
00:15:58,010 --> 00:15:59,150
the best for her child?

284
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:00,940
They wish they could
help the kids onto the horse

285
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:01,910
and see them off properly.

286
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,390
They just hope their path

287
00:16:03,410 --> 00:16:04,540
will take them further

288
00:16:04,560 --> 00:16:05,690
and become wider.

289
00:16:06,700 --> 00:16:07,510
But look at you.

290
00:16:08,150 --> 00:16:08,910
There were no obstacles,

291
00:16:09,010 --> 00:16:09,940
yet you created them for me.

292
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:11,050
Created obstacles?

293
00:16:11,770 --> 00:16:12,390
You think I'd let you go there

294
00:16:12,410 --> 00:16:13,370
