299
00:16:19,100 --> 00:16:20,390
is over 4,000 meters.

300
00:16:20,470 --> 00:16:22,290
The mountain passes are over 5,300 meters.

301
00:16:22,890 --> 00:16:23,630
I've seen

302
00:16:23,660 --> 00:16:24,180
plenty of cases

303
00:16:24,210 --> 00:16:25,100
of sudden altitude sickness.

304
00:16:25,220 --> 00:16:25,770
If you get sick there,

305
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:26,910
no one can save you.

306
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:29,870
It's over 40,000 square kilometers.

307
00:16:29,890 --> 00:16:31,650
They say it's bigger
than 40 Hong Kongs combined.

308
00:16:31,910 --> 00:16:32,870
I've never been to Hong Kong.

309
00:16:32,890 --> 00:16:33,500
And I don't know

310
00:16:33,520 --> 00:16:34,290
how big it is.

311
00:16:34,790 --> 00:16:35,580
But the herdsmen

312
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:36,320
I treat

313
00:16:36,340 --> 00:16:37,290
have never even been there

314
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,500
in their entire lives.

315
00:16:38,620 --> 00:16:39,580
Why don't they go?

316
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,340
First, it's because of their faith.

317
00:16:41,620 --> 00:16:42,170
And also,

318
00:16:42,190 --> 00:16:42,790
they know

319
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:44,340
they can't go in there.

320
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,180
Every time

321
00:16:47,370 --> 00:16:48,620
the Mountain Patrol kids

322
00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:49,340
come by the house,

323
00:16:49,370 --> 00:16:50,670
seeing the way they look,

324
00:16:50,700 --> 00:16:51,500
my heart just sinks.

325
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:52,860
I feel sorry for them,

326
00:16:52,880 --> 00:16:54,560
and I fear for you.

327
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:56,310
I really don't want you

328
00:16:56,340 --> 00:16:57,630
to suffer like that.

329
00:17:00,310 --> 00:17:01,970
Since we're on the subject,

330
00:17:02,530 --> 00:17:04,200
let me tell you, Bai Ju,

331
00:17:04,819 --> 00:17:06,119
don't even think about
entering the mountains.

332
00:17:07,180 --> 00:17:08,030
I won't allow it.

333
00:17:10,250 --> 00:17:11,630
Then why did you support me

334
00:17:11,660 --> 00:17:12,589
when I wanted to go to the police academy

335
00:17:12,910 --> 00:17:14,109
and become a cop back then?

336
00:17:14,430 --> 00:17:15,020
What police officer

337
00:17:15,050 --> 00:17:16,109
doesn't face danger?

338
00:17:16,530 --> 00:17:17,140
Just because

339
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:17,990
the Uninhabited Zone is dangerous,

340
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:19,329
does that mean I should back off?

341
00:17:19,460 --> 00:17:20,530
From the time I was little,

342
00:17:20,660 --> 00:17:21,150
that's not

343
00:17:21,180 --> 00:17:22,109
how you raised me.

344
00:17:22,180 --> 00:17:23,619
I supported you
going to the police academy

345
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:24,650
so that after graduation,

346
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:25,910
you could find a stable job,

347
00:17:25,940 --> 00:17:26,849
like your sister,

348
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:27,869
following a routine and going

349
00:17:27,900 --> 00:17:28,349
to work every day.

350
00:17:28,369 --> 00:17:29,080
My sister is my sister.

351
00:17:29,110 --> 00:17:29,720
I am me.

352
00:17:30,070 --> 00:17:31,030
I'm different from her.

353
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:32,710
Why do you get to decide for me?

354
00:17:33,190 --> 00:17:34,510
Even if you are my real mother,

355
00:17:34,700 --> 00:17:35,810
you shouldn't interfere.

356
00:17:36,090 --> 00:17:36,780
And I certainly don't need you

357
00:17:36,810 --> 00:17:37,940
planning my life.

358
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:39,280
It is precisely
because I am not your biological mother

359
00:17:39,370 --> 00:17:40,630
that I must interfere!

360
00:17:47,810 --> 00:17:48,960
Growing up,

361
00:17:49,820 --> 00:17:50,970
haven't I supported everything

362
00:17:51,690 --> 00:17:53,190
that you wanted to do?

363
00:17:54,420 --> 00:17:55,110
You liked shooting,

364
00:17:55,130 --> 00:17:56,090
so your father took you.

365
00:17:56,500 --> 00:17:57,300
You wanted to be a cop.

366
00:17:57,330 --> 00:17:58,170
Now, you're wearing

367
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:59,070
this uniform.

368
00:17:59,390 --> 00:18:00,440
Is that not enough?

369
00:18:00,610 --> 00:18:01,550
Is it just because I won't let you
have your way

370
00:18:01,570 --> 00:18:03,130
about entering the mountains?

371
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:05,440
I just don't understand

372
00:18:05,460 --> 00:18:06,240
why you must

373
00:18:06,270 --> 00:18:07,400
enter the mountains?

374
00:18:08,990 --> 00:18:10,530
If it were Bai Chun, Bai Ji,

375
00:18:10,610 --> 00:18:11,580
or even Bai Shao,

376
00:18:11,610 --> 00:18:12,530
I wouldn't interfere.

377
00:18:12,770 --> 00:18:14,180
But with you, I have to step in.

378
00:18:14,440 --> 00:18:15,540
Because your biological parents

379
00:18:15,570 --> 00:18:16,610
are watching me from heaven.

380
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:18,250
If anything happened to you,

381
00:18:18,270 --> 00:18:19,670
I couldn't face them.

382
00:18:35,720 --> 00:18:36,400
Call Mom for dinner.

383
00:18:50,430 --> 00:18:50,960
Mom,

384
00:18:53,250 --> 00:18:53,960
dinner is ready.

385
00:19:11,840 --> 00:19:12,920
That's too much, Shi Long.

386
00:19:14,250 --> 00:19:15,640
The Party Secretary
and County Mayor just agreed

387
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:16,800
to give the Mountain Patrol

388
00:19:16,830 --> 00:19:17,480
more weapon support.

389
00:19:18,450 --> 00:19:19,740
Why are you giving us less?

390
00:19:20,420 --> 00:19:21,090
Just one pistol

391
00:19:21,110 --> 00:19:21,830
and two boxes of ammo.

392
00:19:22,310 --> 00:19:23,360
How do you expect me to sign for this?

393
00:19:24,110 --> 00:19:24,590
Hey,

394
00:19:24,610 --> 00:19:25,740
listen to me.

395
00:19:25,940 --> 00:19:26,570
The new ammo

396
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:27,810
we requested

397
00:19:27,830 --> 00:19:28,890
is still on the way.

398
00:19:29,290 --> 00:19:29,870
As for those two

399
00:19:29,900 --> 00:19:30,790
semi-automatic rifles,

400
00:19:31,260 --> 00:19:32,390
the municipal bureau hasn't approved them.

401
00:19:32,420 --> 00:19:33,350
No approval means no approval, so...

402
00:19:33,750 --> 00:19:34,350
you know.

403
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:35,370
We've seized

404
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:36,420
plenty of firearms and ammunition before.

405
00:19:37,510 --> 00:19:38,180
In storage…

406
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:40,710
Well,

407
00:19:40,740 --> 00:19:41,520
the non-standard ones

408
00:19:41,550 --> 00:19:42,590
were all destroyed.

409
00:19:42,610 --> 00:19:43,480
And the rest

410
00:19:45,610 --> 00:19:46,480
were distributed.

411
00:19:46,880 --> 00:19:47,870
I can't go to the comrades

412
00:19:47,900 --> 00:19:48,880
and ask for them back, right?

413
00:19:49,430 --> 00:19:50,370
You sold them, didn't you?

414
00:19:51,220 --> 00:19:52,720
You can't say that!

415
00:19:53,030 --> 00:19:53,420
Well.

416
00:19:53,980 --> 00:19:54,500
There were

417
00:19:54,540 --> 00:19:55,500
indeed a few

418
00:19:55,570 --> 00:19:56,420
in good condition,

419
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:56,930
but they've already

420
00:19:56,960 --> 00:19:58,310
been reassigned to other units.

421
00:19:58,530 --> 00:19:58,710
This...

422
00:19:58,800 --> 00:20:00,020
This was decided
by the Bureau Party Committee.

423
00:20:00,050 --> 00:20:01,200
I didn't do it on my own.

424
00:20:01,550 --> 00:20:02,130
You were at the meeting.

425
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:02,920
You know that.

426
00:20:03,030 --> 00:20:03,570
I know.

427
00:20:03,660 --> 00:20:04,200
Hey.

428
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:05,420
Really.

429
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:06,810
I still have to

430
00:20:06,830 --> 00:20:08,030
keep my position.

431
00:20:09,100 --> 00:20:09,780
So,

432
00:20:10,530 --> 00:20:12,030
please just sign it.

433
00:20:12,290 --> 00:20:12,920
Come on.

434
00:20:13,300 --> 00:20:14,130
Sign it.

435
00:20:14,840 --> 00:20:15,900
Thank you. Thank you.

436
00:20:18,240 --> 00:20:18,940
Don't worry.

437
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:19,850
As soon as the ammo arrives,

438
00:20:19,870 --> 00:20:20,760
I'll send someone

439
00:20:20,790 --> 00:20:21,440
to bring it to you immediately.

440
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:22,610
I'm anxious, too,

441
00:20:22,630 --> 00:20:23,260
you know.

442
00:20:25,330 --> 00:20:26,380
Just sign it.

443
00:20:27,150 --> 00:20:27,760
Thanks.

444
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:34,590
It's getting late.

445
00:20:34,700 --> 00:20:35,610
We should go eat.

446
00:20:36,590 --> 00:20:37,460
The meal is on me later.

447
00:20:37,810 --> 00:20:39,010
I found a noodle place.

448
00:20:39,040 --> 00:20:39,930
Their pulled noodles are even better

449
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:41,250
than my wife's.

450
00:20:41,380 --> 00:20:42,070
Come on, let's go.

451
00:20:42,090 --> 00:20:42,920
Let's get the stuff first.

452
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:43,510
Get the stuff.

453
00:20:43,660 --> 00:20:44,050
Let's go.

454
00:20:57,420 --> 00:20:58,140
Come on, get out!

455
00:20:58,900 --> 00:20:59,470
Behave yourself.

456
00:21:01,320 --> 00:21:01,820
Chief.

457
00:21:04,010 --> 00:21:04,660
Who is this?

458
00:21:05,070 --> 00:21:05,880
At the road checkpoint,

459
00:21:05,920 --> 00:21:07,160
we stopped a pickup truck.

460
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:09,260
Based on the suspect's

461
00:21:09,290 --> 00:21:09,980
physical description,

462
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:10,850
I suspect

463
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:12,010
he's the fugitive, Guo Shun.

464
00:21:13,220 --> 00:21:13,770
Where's the truck?

465
00:21:14,570 --> 00:21:15,590
That truck's got a carburetor problem,

466
00:21:15,610 --> 00:21:16,260
so it drives slowly.

467
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:17,400
We brought him back first.

468
00:21:18,030 --> 00:21:18,740
Hey,

469
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:19,550
Comrades,

470
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:21,440
you've got the wrong person.

471
00:21:21,960 --> 00:21:23,480
I'm just a transporter.

472
00:21:23,850 --> 00:21:24,900
The stuff on that truck

473
00:21:24,920 --> 00:21:25,770
isn't mine.

474
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:27,950
And I don't know anything

475
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:29,350
about what you're saying.

476
00:21:30,350 --> 00:21:31,000
Guo Shun.

477
00:21:31,760 --> 00:21:32,400
Do you think no one

478
00:21:32,430 --> 00:21:33,850
in Mazhi County knows who you are?

479
00:21:34,440 --> 00:21:35,560
Do you want me to bring Bai Ji

480
00:21:35,590 --> 00:21:36,500
out of the detention center

481
00:21:36,520 --> 00:21:37,260
to identify you?

482
00:21:38,070 --> 00:21:38,740
You sent the skinners

483
00:21:38,770 --> 00:21:39,720
into Bolamula,

484
00:21:39,810 --> 00:21:41,010
didn't you?

485
00:21:42,370 --> 00:21:43,570
We're looking for your boss.

486
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:46,550
I don't have a boss.

487
00:21:46,850 --> 00:21:48,440
I just do odd jobs

488
00:21:48,460 --> 00:21:49,370
and small businesses

489
00:21:49,400 --> 00:21:50,500
to make a living.

490
00:21:54,310 --> 00:21:55,110
Chief Shi.

491
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:56,910
This suspect

492
00:21:56,940 --> 00:21:58,070
is being very uncooperative with you.

493
00:21:59,140 --> 00:21:59,960
I think you should send him

494
00:21:59,980 --> 00:22:00,810
to my place.

495
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:04,090
The kids in the Mountain Patrol

496
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:05,920
have ways to make him talk.

497
00:22:06,980 --> 00:22:08,240
I guess that's our only option.

498
00:22:09,050 --> 00:22:09,770
You two,

499
00:22:09,820 --> 00:22:10,640
take him and go
with Deputy County Mayor Duo.

500
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:11,160
Yes, sir.

501
00:22:11,330 --> 00:22:12,080
What are you doing?

502
00:22:12,110 --> 00:22:12,570
Move!

503
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:13,080
Let go!

504
00:22:13,110 --> 00:22:13,330
Stand up!

505
00:22:13,350 --> 00:22:14,180
I'm not going anywhere!

506
00:22:14,720 --> 00:22:15,940
I'm not going anywhere!

507
00:22:16,740 --> 00:22:17,290
Let me go.

508
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:18,680
I'm not going anywhere!

509
00:22:21,620 --> 00:22:22,320
You blew up

510
00:22:22,350 --> 00:22:23,240
our warehouse.

511
00:22:24,120 --> 00:22:24,560
Not long ago,

512
00:22:24,590 --> 00:22:25,740
we lost a member.

513
00:22:26,140 --> 00:22:27,340
He was only 18.

514
00:22:28,530 --> 00:22:29,820
If you want to redeem yourself,

515
00:22:30,330 --> 00:22:31,000
give up your boss

516
00:22:31,020 --> 00:22:31,830
and tell us everything.

517
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:33,660
Otherwise,

518
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,220
I'm pinning all of this on you.

519
00:22:36,030 --> 00:22:36,610
Who do you

520
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:38,140
think you are?

521
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:39,470
Everyone in the county knows

522
00:22:39,500 --> 00:22:40,940
you've lost your mind.

523
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:42,000
If you hadn't

524
00:22:42,030 --> 00:22:43,140
insisted on taking people
into the mountains,

525
00:22:43,240 --> 00:22:44,070
would anyone

526
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:45,000
have died?

527
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:46,860
Everyone would've made their money.

528
00:22:47,220 --> 00:22:47,850
Let me tell you.

529
00:22:48,090 --> 00:22:48,820
That member of yours

530
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:49,970
died because of you,

531
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:50,690
you bastard.

532
00:22:50,720 --> 00:22:51,160
Say that again!

533
00:22:52,030 --> 00:22:53,060
Come on, hit me.

534
00:22:53,090 --> 00:22:53,720
Kill me!

535
00:22:53,830 --> 00:22:54,130
Calm down.

536
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:55,020
Deputy County Mayor Duo!

537
00:22:55,050 --> 00:22:55,850
Deputy County Mayor Duo is hitting people!

538
00:22:55,870 --> 00:22:56,550
Deputy County Mayor Duo.

539
00:22:56,660 --> 00:22:56,950
Calm down.

540
00:22:56,980 --> 00:22:57,830
Are you police going to stop him?

541
00:22:57,850 --> 00:22:58,610
Calm down!

542
00:22:58,630 --> 00:22:59,090
Behave yourself!

543
00:22:59,200 --> 00:22:59,590
Are you going to stop him?

544
00:22:59,610 --> 00:23:00,240
Behave yourself.

545
00:23:00,330 --> 00:23:00,570
Are you...

546
00:23:00,750 --> 00:23:01,440
What are you doing?

547
00:23:02,350 --> 00:23:03,130
What are you doing?

548
00:23:04,030 --> 00:23:05,030
You're out of line!

549
00:23:08,180 --> 00:23:08,940
What did you find in the car?

550
00:23:09,510 --> 00:23:10,030
Explosives

551
00:23:10,250 --> 00:23:10,960
and bullets.

552
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:24,010
There are at least a thousand rounds here.

553
00:23:24,460 --> 00:23:25,340
A thousand rounds...

554
00:23:28,500 --> 00:23:29,650
Fifty jins.

555
00:23:32,970 --> 00:23:34,120
These fifty jins of bullets

556
00:23:34,290 --> 00:23:35,510
aren't for hunting the antelopes.

557
00:23:37,010 --> 00:23:38,170
Explain yourself.

558
00:23:40,590 --> 00:23:41,910
They're meant for you.

559
00:23:55,500 --> 00:23:56,530
You've got some premature beats,

560
00:23:56,620 --> 00:23:57,400
but nothing serious.

561
00:23:57,900 --> 00:23:59,470
Stay in the hospital
for observation for two days.

562
00:23:59,570 --> 00:24:00,740
I don't need to stay, do I?

563
00:24:01,250 --> 00:24:02,180
It's an old problem.

564
00:24:02,510 --> 00:24:03,220
When I don't rest well,

565
00:24:03,240 --> 00:24:04,350
it tends to happen.

566
00:24:04,510 --> 00:24:06,420
Lin is just worrying for nothing.

567
00:24:07,350 --> 00:24:09,270
The heart is no small matter.

568
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:10,630
You must take it seriously.

569
00:24:11,310 --> 00:24:13,440
If there's a problem,
you need medical treatment right away.

570
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:14,850
Lin did the right thing.

571
00:24:14,880 --> 00:24:15,580
Listen to that.

572
00:24:16,110 --> 00:24:17,240
Listen to that.

573
00:24:17,850 --> 00:24:19,220
If you're told to come, just come.

574
00:24:19,240 --> 00:24:20,410
Listen to Director Zhang.

575
00:24:21,450 --> 00:24:22,770
Stop writing.

576
00:24:22,870 --> 00:24:24,070
Talk to us.

577
00:24:24,980 --> 00:24:26,320
Wasn't it enough
to write it up in the office?

578
00:24:26,350 --> 00:24:27,850
You had to bring it to the hospital, too?

579
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:29,810
In the whole county, no one's busier

580
00:24:29,840 --> 00:24:31,030
or more capable than you.

581
00:24:31,790 --> 00:24:32,880
This report

582
00:24:32,980 --> 00:24:34,070
needs more work.

583
00:24:34,380 --> 00:24:35,300
Last time
the Municipal People's Congress mentioned

584
00:24:35,330 --> 00:24:36,970
they still need to assess
the snowstorm damage in the county

585
00:24:37,480 --> 00:24:38,290
I plan

586
00:24:38,400 --> 00:24:39,640
to go to the city government again

587
00:24:40,610 --> 00:24:42,250
and submit a detailed report.

588
00:24:42,440 --> 00:24:44,500
Our county has no industry.

589
00:24:45,030 --> 00:24:45,700
The largest portion

590
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:47,200
of profit and tax this year

591
00:24:47,380 --> 00:24:48,640
came from the animal husbandry tax.

592
00:24:48,670 --> 00:24:50,150
You want to reduce even this?

593
00:24:51,050 --> 00:24:53,010
That put the city leaders
in a tough spot, too.

594
00:24:53,180 --> 00:24:54,660
I support Lin on this.

595
00:24:55,250 --> 00:24:55,830
I receive patients

596
00:24:55,850 --> 00:24:56,930
from the pastoral areas every day.

597
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:57,700
I know

598
00:24:58,160 --> 00:24:59,720
that after this year's snow disaster,

599
00:24:59,920 --> 00:25:01,440
the herdsmen are really struggling.

600
00:25:08,300 --> 00:25:09,200
In the end,

601
00:25:09,330 --> 00:25:10,580
our county's conditions

602
00:25:10,610 --> 00:25:11,510
are simply too poor.

603
00:25:12,960 --> 00:25:13,640
Lin,

604
00:25:14,380 --> 00:25:15,500
tell us,

605
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:17,200
when will our county

606
00:25:17,220 --> 00:25:18,570
get rich?

607
00:25:26,850 --> 00:25:28,680
Just say our county‘s economy

608
00:25:29,310 --> 00:25:30,020
is fixated

609
00:25:30,050 --> 00:25:32,070
on cows and sheep,
working them to the bone.

610
00:25:32,740 --> 00:25:33,260
But the herdsmen

611
00:25:33,290 --> 00:25:34,680
are reluctant to sell.

612
00:25:35,440 --> 00:25:36,980
And they like
to compare livestock numbers.

613
00:25:38,740 --> 00:25:39,980
Except for the required

614
00:25:40,070 --> 00:25:41,400
beef cattle and mutton sheep,

615
00:25:41,500 --> 00:25:43,010
they won't sell a single one of the rest.

616
00:25:44,010 --> 00:25:44,640
At the beginning of the year,

617
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:46,200
a snow disaster

618
00:25:46,610 --> 00:25:48,070
killed or injured more than half.

619
00:25:48,770 --> 00:25:49,610
Even now, the stock numbers

620
00:25:49,630 --> 00:25:50,310
haven't recovered.

621
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:54,980
Director Zhang,

622
00:25:55,070 --> 00:25:56,570
there's a patient. Come take a look.

623
00:25:56,590 --> 00:25:57,550
Okay, coming.

624
00:25:58,030 --> 00:25:58,980
I'll go take a look.

625
00:25:59,570 --> 00:26:00,530
Light

626
00:26:00,940 --> 00:26:01,610
that gas lamp up.

627
00:26:01,670 --> 00:26:02,720
It's almost ten-thirty.

628
00:26:02,740 --> 00:26:03,480
You carry on.

629
00:26:12,430 --> 00:26:13,410
You...

630
00:26:13,740 --> 00:26:14,780
Director Zhang was here just now,

631
00:26:14,810 --> 00:26:15,830
so I didn't want to bring it up.

632
00:26:16,330 --> 00:26:17,370
Don't you think about

633
00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:18,880
your own career development?

634
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:21,640
Right now,

635
00:26:21,700 --> 00:26:22,700
in your leadership team,

636
00:26:22,720 --> 00:26:24,200
you're the most educated

637
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:25,460
and the youngest.

638
00:26:26,330 --> 00:26:28,510
If there's another promotion coming up,

639
00:26:28,690 --> 00:26:30,940
it'll be you.

640
00:26:31,590 --> 00:26:32,880
Do you have to

641
00:26:32,900 --> 00:26:34,320
upset the leadership right now?

642
00:26:35,090 --> 00:26:36,680
Jianshe is graduating next year.

643
00:26:36,700 --> 00:26:38,260
I was hoping you could pull some strings

644
00:26:38,430 --> 00:26:39,260
to find him an internship

645
00:26:39,290 --> 00:26:40,350
in the city.

646
00:26:40,370 --> 00:26:42,150
He's not graduating
until next year, right?

647
00:26:42,590 --> 00:26:43,570
What's the rush?

648
00:26:45,110 --> 00:26:45,880
Besides,

649
00:26:46,610 --> 00:26:47,110
am I not even allowed to speak up

650
00:26:47,130 --> 00:26:48,220
because of all that?

651
00:26:53,140 --> 00:26:53,930
Duojie said something

652
00:26:53,960 --> 00:26:54,770
that was really good.

653
00:26:55,740 --> 00:26:57,240
The situation in the county

654
00:26:57,270 --> 00:26:58,940
is like a piece of lean meat.

655
00:26:59,270 --> 00:27:00,000
If you try to scrape fat from it,

656
00:27:00,030 --> 00:27:01,070
you won't get any.

657
00:27:12,510 --> 00:27:14,160
Given our county's situation,

658
00:27:15,070 --> 00:27:15,630
the fact

659
00:27:15,660 --> 00:27:16,850
that you've kept things stable here,

660
00:27:16,870 --> 00:27:17,890
without any incidents,

661
00:27:19,550 --> 00:27:21,070
that alone counts as an achievement.

662
00:27:24,270 --> 00:27:25,000
Ms. Zhu,

663
00:27:26,050 --> 00:27:26,970
your level

664
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:28,350
keeps getting higher and higher.

665
00:27:28,900 --> 00:27:29,730
What you just said

666
00:27:29,920 --> 00:27:31,110
is exactly the same

667
00:27:31,130 --> 00:27:32,410
as what you said
when the Governor

668
00:27:32,430 --> 00:27:34,290
visited last year.

669
00:27:39,900 --> 00:27:41,180
We're almost done interrogating Shi Long.

670
00:27:42,250 --> 00:27:43,700
We're preparing to enter the mountains
in ten days.

671
00:27:45,270 --> 00:27:46,670
Did he give up the meeting location too?

672
00:27:47,890 --> 00:27:49,310
If things go our way,

673
00:27:50,020 --> 00:27:50,670
we're going

674
00:27:50,700 --> 00:27:51,670
to nail the guy

675
00:27:51,700 --> 00:27:52,250
who killed Dongzhiba.

676
00:27:52,700 --> 00:27:54,050
Don't just focus on making arrests.

677
00:27:54,360 --> 00:27:55,060
At the last meeting,

678
00:27:55,090 --> 00:27:55,840
the Party Secretary said—

679
00:27:55,870 --> 00:27:56,810
I remember that.

680
00:27:57,700 --> 00:27:58,980
I won't forget
about the mineral exploration.

681
00:28:03,290 --> 00:28:04,140
Shi told me

682
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:06,440
you took twenty-five jins of bullets.

683
00:28:08,980 --> 00:28:09,750
The Party Secretary also mentioned

684
00:28:09,770 --> 00:28:10,510
at the meeting

685
00:28:11,170 --> 00:28:12,170
that we will have full authority

686
00:28:12,200 --> 00:28:12,880
over the use

687
00:28:12,980 --> 00:28:14,240
of any seized firearms and ammunition.

688
00:28:14,330 --> 00:28:15,060
I said that, too.

689
00:28:15,090 --> 00:28:16,070
Yes.

690
00:28:16,980 --> 00:28:18,090
Hey, you can't jump

691
00:28:18,110 --> 00:28:19,000
into fight mode every time

692
00:28:19,030 --> 00:28:20,030
someone says something, alright?

693
00:28:20,660 --> 00:28:20,850
Stop...

694
00:28:20,870 --> 00:28:22,000
Stop wearing that look
on your face all the time,

695
00:28:22,030 --> 00:28:22,640
okay?

696
00:28:25,070 --> 00:28:26,240
I really don't like chatting with you.

697
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:28,350
You've already said everything
there is to say.

698
00:28:28,830 --> 00:28:29,220
Isn't he just

699
00:28:29,250 --> 00:28:30,090
annoyed because I took too much?

700
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:31,780
Shi said those bullets

701
00:28:31,810 --> 00:28:32,880
were all meant

702
00:28:32,900 --> 00:28:33,640
for your Mountain Patrol.

703
00:28:33,660 --> 00:28:33,980
He was surprised

704
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:35,180
you still left half for them.

705
00:28:38,840 --> 00:28:39,640
That's good then.

706
00:28:40,510 --> 00:28:40,940
I...

707
00:28:41,030 --> 00:28:41,980
I'll have Bai Ju

708
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:42,850
go back to the bureau
to get them tomorrow.

709
00:28:43,030 --> 00:28:43,600
I agree.

710
00:28:44,070 --> 00:28:44,700
I support that.

711
00:28:47,550 --> 00:28:48,570
There's one more thing

712
00:28:49,390 --> 00:28:50,570
I need you to handle.

713
00:28:54,150 --> 00:28:55,330
You, the leader, said I look grim

714
00:28:55,410 --> 00:28:56,740
and have an attitude.

715
00:28:58,090 --> 00:28:59,270
So I'll accept the task with a smile,

716
00:28:59,550 --> 00:29:00,270
happy now?

717
00:29:01,810 --> 00:29:02,710
What do you want me to do?

718
00:29:05,790 --> 00:29:07,670
I got someone to contact

719
00:29:07,700 --> 00:29:09,310
a reporter
from the Provincial Evening News.

720
00:29:09,740 --> 00:29:10,830
And a few entrepreneurs

721
00:29:10,870 --> 00:29:13,130
who are interested
in our county's mining industry

722
00:29:13,310 --> 00:29:15,200
and intend to invest.

723
00:29:16,640 --> 00:29:17,510
In a few days,

724
00:29:18,050 --> 00:29:19,050
they'll come to our county together

725
00:29:19,070 --> 00:29:20,130
for a site visit.

726
00:29:22,380 --> 00:29:23,250
Look, look, look.

727
00:29:23,350 --> 00:29:24,260
You're showing that attitude again,

728
00:29:24,290 --> 00:29:24,670
aren't you?

729
00:29:24,700 --> 00:29:25,040
No way.

730
00:29:25,070 --> 00:29:25,940
I've been smiling the whole time.

731
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:26,500
Yes.

732
00:29:26,620 --> 00:29:27,710
You had a beautiful smile.

733
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:31,310
This counts as our county's

734
00:29:31,330 --> 00:29:32,720
investment promotion meeting.

735
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:33,530
We have to let the outside world

736
00:29:33,550 --> 00:29:34,720
get to know us.

737
00:29:35,180 --> 00:29:36,460
We must fire

738
00:29:36,660 --> 00:29:37,500
our county's

739
00:29:37,590 --> 00:29:38,960
first shot in mining development.

740
00:29:38,980 --> 00:29:39,690
Don't mention

741
00:29:39,720 --> 00:29:40,530
the word "shot" to me.

742
00:29:41,220 --> 00:29:42,200
It gives me a headache.

743
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:45,310
How about this?

744
00:29:45,940 --> 00:29:46,510
How about this?

745
00:29:47,460 --> 00:29:48,550
Let's strive to take

746
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:50,890
Mazhi County's

747
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:53,500
first step in mining development.

748
00:29:55,070 --> 00:29:55,570
Is that okay?

749
00:29:56,140 --> 00:29:57,530
Is that okay? Is that okay?

750
00:29:59,080 --> 00:30:00,080
What do you need me to do?

751
00:30:08,990 --> 00:30:10,150
This smile isn't bad.

752
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:16,920
I suggest we arrange the site visit

753
00:30:16,940 --> 00:30:18,240
at Wulan Canyon.

754
00:30:19,910 --> 00:30:21,590
The altitude there is 4,200 meters.

755
00:30:22,350 --> 00:30:23,130
Why don't you arrange it

756
00:30:23,160 --> 00:30:24,000
at Baozi Canyon?

757
00:30:24,020 --> 00:30:24,970
That's 4,700 meters.

758
00:30:27,190 --> 00:30:27,900
That works, too.

759
00:30:28,480 --> 00:30:28,970
Baozi Canyon

760
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:30,530
is on the outskirts of Bolamula.

761
00:30:30,660 --> 00:30:32,090
There's even more to see there.

762
00:30:33,310 --> 00:30:34,680
Good. Baozi Canyon is good.

763
00:30:35,530 --> 00:30:36,040
It is pretty good.

764
00:30:36,070 --> 00:30:36,960
What's so good about it?

765
00:30:37,530 --> 00:30:38,610
County Mayor Lin asked us to arrange

766
00:30:38,640 --> 00:30:39,330
the inspection route.

767
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:40,380
You set it up at such a high altitude,

768
00:30:40,410 --> 00:30:41,610
aren't you undermining him?

769
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:42,270
Exactly.

770
00:30:42,660 --> 00:30:43,770
The Captain is right.

771
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:44,610
It's so high.

772
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:45,770
Can they handle it?

773
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:48,080
Why are you such a flip-flopper?

774
00:30:49,510 --> 00:30:50,400
It's a fact.

775
00:30:52,250 --> 00:30:53,050
Are they here for tourism

776
00:30:53,070 --> 00:30:54,070
or for an inspection?

777
00:30:54,660 --> 00:30:55,250
Only by getting close

778
00:30:55,270 --> 00:30:56,340
to the Bolamula Uninhabited Zone

779
00:30:56,470 --> 00:30:57,810
can they find mineral resources.

780
00:30:58,530 --> 00:30:59,190
In the future,

781
00:30:59,220 --> 00:31:00,880
if they want to develop Bolamula,

782
00:31:00,980 --> 00:31:02,530
the altitude inside will only be higher.

783
00:31:03,640 --> 00:31:04,690
These two spots now

784
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:06,250
are just small potatoes.

785
00:31:08,490 --> 00:31:09,230
What are you laughing at?

786
00:31:09,750 --> 00:31:11,030
That's just how it's said in Cantonese.

787
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:12,680
What does it mean?

788
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:13,870
It just

789
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:15,440
means “no big deal.”

790
00:31:18,900 --> 00:31:19,400
Anyway,

791
00:31:19,420 --> 00:31:20,220
if they can't

792
00:31:20,250 --> 00:31:21,160
even handle this,

793
00:31:21,590 --> 00:31:22,980
how are they going to survey

794
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:23,980
or mine later on?

795
00:31:26,330 --> 00:31:27,460
We could take them

796
00:31:27,480 --> 00:31:28,800
to a lower altitude for a tour.

797
00:31:29,830 --> 00:31:30,640
But then they won't see

798
00:31:30,660 --> 00:31:31,550
the reality.

799
00:31:31,620 --> 00:31:32,240
Then what's the point

800
00:31:32,270 --> 00:31:33,240
of a site visit?

801
00:31:33,750 --> 00:31:34,400
Then we'd really be

802
00:31:34,510 --> 00:31:35,000
undermining

803
00:31:35,030 --> 00:31:36,070
County Mayor Lin.

804
00:31:39,800 --> 00:31:40,840
You're right.

805
00:31:41,850 --> 00:31:43,010
Let's do it your way.

806
00:31:44,240 --> 00:31:44,850
We'll set it up

807
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:46,460
in the outer areas of Bolamula.

808
00:31:46,960 --> 00:31:47,850
Small potatoes.

809
00:31:50,510 --> 00:31:50,960
Okay.

810
00:31:52,440 --> 00:31:53,330
Alright, stop laughing.

811
00:31:53,910 --> 00:31:55,240
Hurry up and make a budget.

812
00:31:55,330 --> 00:31:55,870
Make a spreadsheet.

813
00:31:55,900 --> 00:31:56,350
Okay.

814
00:31:57,510 --> 00:31:58,700
As long as this development company

815
00:31:58,720 --> 00:31:59,720
can get off the ground,

816
00:31:59,880 --> 00:32:01,290
whether it's Liu or Jiumei,

817
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:02,480
I can bring them back.

818
00:32:44,090 --> 00:32:44,850
This one?

819
00:32:44,870 --> 00:32:46,310
Name your price.

820
00:32:48,940 --> 00:32:50,240
How about this much?

821
00:32:50,710 --> 00:32:51,580
I'll offer this much.

822
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:57,240
The price has to be reasonable.

823
00:32:57,270 --> 00:32:58,440
If it's not, there's no point.

824
00:33:00,030 --> 00:33:00,880
Fine, fine.

825
00:33:10,010 --> 00:33:10,730
Okay.

826
00:33:13,290 --> 00:33:13,740
Bai Ji.

827
00:33:14,350 --> 00:33:15,060
You scared me.

828
00:33:15,140 --> 00:33:15,970
What's wrong with you?

829
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:17,030
You didn't even eat breakfast.

830
00:33:17,700 --> 00:33:18,100
Here.

831
00:33:18,480 --> 00:33:19,270
Eat the egg.

832
00:33:23,610 --> 00:33:24,770
What are you doing now?

833
00:33:25,770 --> 00:33:27,100
You have a job now.

834
00:33:27,210 --> 00:33:28,240
Pull yourself together

835
00:33:28,270 --> 00:33:29,640
and work hard, okay?

836
00:33:30,930 --> 00:33:32,300
What kind of job is this—

837
00:33:33,460 --> 00:33:34,040
Sweeping streets

838
00:33:34,070 --> 00:33:34,980
and dumping trash.

839
00:33:35,920 --> 00:33:37,250
I have to clean the toilets later.

840
00:33:37,600 --> 00:33:38,210
After that,

841
00:33:38,240 --> 00:33:39,640
I have to help in the kitchen.

842
00:33:43,410 --> 00:33:43,960
Sis,

843
00:33:44,350 --> 00:33:45,160
these two jobs,

844
00:33:45,180 --> 00:33:46,650
shouldn't be done
by the same person, right?

845
00:33:54,080 --> 00:33:55,120
Stop talking nonsense.

846
00:33:56,010 --> 00:33:57,160
Just do what you're told.

847
00:33:58,030 --> 00:33:59,450
Quit your whining.

848
00:33:59,730 --> 00:34:00,430
Behave yourself,

849
00:34:00,460 --> 00:34:01,770
or I'll have your second sister
deal with you.

850
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:02,640
Got it?

851
00:34:03,890 --> 00:34:04,350
Eat it.

852
00:34:12,920 --> 00:34:14,070
Okay. Bye.

853
00:34:14,090 --> 00:34:14,780
Okay, okay.

854
00:34:14,850 --> 00:34:16,040
Then it's a deal between us.

855
00:34:16,150 --> 00:34:17,210
It's a deal.

856
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:18,560
Let me introduce you.

857
00:34:18,590 --> 00:34:19,510
This is our newly appointed Member

858
00:34:19,530 --> 00:34:20,800
of the County Party Standing Committee
and Head of the Organization Department.

859
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:22,260
Take care. Tashi Delek.

860
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:23,170
Tashi Delek.

861
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:24,449
This is our...

862
00:34:24,480 --> 00:34:25,420
Open the window.

863
00:34:25,659 --> 00:34:25,980
Dad.

864
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:26,620
Later, they...

865
00:34:26,820 --> 00:34:27,190
Okay.

866
00:34:27,300 --> 00:34:27,780
I'm ready.

867
00:34:27,860 --> 00:34:28,510
Come here.

868
00:34:29,650 --> 00:34:30,800
Let me introduce you.

869
00:34:31,550 --> 00:34:32,469
This is my son.

870
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:34,170
Deputy County Mayor Duojie.

871
00:34:34,190 --> 00:34:35,190
Deputy County Mayor Duojie.

872
00:34:35,360 --> 00:34:35,880
Hello.

873
00:34:36,590 --> 00:34:37,840
Isn't this supposed
to be an inspection team?

874
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:40,730
Why are there so few people?

875
00:34:43,460 --> 00:34:44,770
It's good enough that we have these few.

876
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:46,010
Be grateful.

877
00:34:46,040 --> 00:34:46,929
Altitude sickness is like that.

878
00:34:47,980 --> 00:34:48,820
I don't need it.

879
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:50,400
If anything comes up later,

880
00:34:50,500 --> 00:34:51,060
you can get to

881
00:34:51,090 --> 00:34:52,150
the Mountain Patrol members.

882
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:54,560
They are very experienced

883
00:34:54,590 --> 00:34:55,610
on the plateau.

884
00:34:59,150 --> 00:35:00,300
I'll go get ready.

885
00:35:00,320 --> 00:35:01,010
See you later.

886
00:35:01,160 --> 00:35:01,480
Okay.

