Should we keep waiting?

924
00:36:24,980 --> 00:36:25,480
Everyone.

925
00:36:26,030 --> 00:36:26,510
Everyone.

926
00:36:26,610 --> 00:36:27,570
There's no time to lose.

927
00:36:28,210 --> 00:36:29,250
Let's hurry up

928
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:30,150
