934
00:36:36,730 --> 00:36:37,230
Get in the car.

935
00:36:37,640 --> 00:36:38,000
Okay.

936
00:36:38,510 --> 00:36:38,980
Let's go.

937
00:36:40,900 --> 00:36:41,590
Okay.

938
00:36:42,070 --> 00:36:42,650
