941
00:36:45,120 --> 00:36:45,480
Okay.

942
00:36:51,690 --> 00:36:52,320
Come here.

943
00:36:52,940 --> 00:36:53,690
Everyone, follow me.

944
00:36:54,330 --> 00:36:55,080
Look over here.

945
00:36:56,320 --> 00:36:57,670
The next phase of the plan

946
00:36:58,300 --> 00:36:59,340
is to move in from here

947
00:36:59,710 --> 00:37:00,280
into

948
00:37:00,300 --> 00:37:01,590
the interior of Bolamula

949
00:37:01,800 --> 00:37:03,150
and carry out on-site geological surveys.

950
00:37:04,090 --> 00:37:04,420
Based on

951
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:05,980
preliminary findings,

952
00:37:06,400 --> 00:37:07,680
this area contains

953
00:37:08,190 --> 00:37:08,920
chromium,

954
00:37:09,420 --> 00:37:10,150
lithium,

955
00:37:10,570 --> 00:37:11,500
and placer gold deposits.

956
00:37:11,690 --> 00:37:12,330
County Mayor Lin,

957
00:37:13,690 --> 00:37:14,880
about

958
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:16,420
the exploration report

959
00:37:16,690 --> 00:37:18,320
we discussed last time,

960
00:37:18,550 --> 00:37:19,820
