961
00:37:20,450 --> 00:37:21,200
Exactly.

962
00:37:23,030 --> 00:37:23,780
Exactly.

963
00:37:26,120 --> 00:37:27,120
Over the past year,

964
00:37:27,350 --> 00:37:29,290
under the leadership
of Deputy County Mayor Duojie,

965
00:37:29,460 --> 00:37:30,390
the Mountain Patrol

966
00:37:30,420 --> 00:37:31,340
of the Mazhi Economic

967
00:37:31,360 --> 00:37:31,970
Development Company

968
00:37:32,150 --> 00:37:33,060
has entered the interior

969
00:37:33,090 --> 00:37:34,110
of Bolamula multiple times

970
00:37:34,190 --> 00:37:35,630
to conduct field surveys.

971
00:37:36,940 --> 00:37:37,960
In at most five months,

972
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:40,080
we will submit a relatively comprehensive

973
00:37:40,110 --> 00:37:41,570
mineral exploration report to everyone.

974
00:37:42,110 --> 00:37:43,010
Five months?

975
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:44,620
That's almost half a year.

976
00:37:45,420 --> 00:37:46,130
The time is too long.

977
00:37:50,510 --> 00:37:51,050
Then...

978
00:37:52,420 --> 00:37:53,050
Three months.

979
00:37:58,400 --> 00:37:58,940
In three months,

980
00:37:59,300 --> 00:38:00,240
you'll definitely see

981
00:38:00,270 --> 00:38:01,270
the mineral exploration report.

982
00:38:02,760 --> 00:38:03,090
Come on,

983
00:38:03,190 --> 00:38:04,190
look here, everyone.

984
00:38:04,780 --> 00:38:05,270
This mountain

985
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:06,820
right in front of us

986
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:07,580
contains rich

987
00:38:07,610 --> 00:38:09,670
oil shale reserves.

988
00:38:10,030 --> 00:38:11,440
Oil shale extraction

989
00:38:11,530 --> 00:38:12,790
has already been adopted

990
00:38:12,820 --> 00:38:14,400
in many regions.

991
00:38:14,510 --> 00:38:15,320
You could say

992
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:16,840
that in the mining industry,

993
00:38:16,860 --> 00:38:19,030
it is a highly high-profile resource

994
00:38:35,300 --> 00:38:35,690
The...

995
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:36,620
The elevation

996
00:38:36,650 --> 00:38:37,590
here isn't high—

997
00:38:37,610 --> 00:38:39,130
just around 4,500 meters.

998
00:38:40,190 --> 00:38:41,650
It lies on the edge

999
00:38:41,670 --> 00:38:42,890
of the county-designated development zone.

1000
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:44,260
Geological conditions here

1001
00:38:44,280 --> 00:38:45,110
are favorable.

1002
00:38:45,260 --> 00:38:46,090
Winds are mild in winter,

1003
00:38:46,110 --> 00:38:46,960
