1004
00:38:47,190 --> 00:38:47,800
so the mining season

1005
00:38:47,860 --> 00:38:48,690
can be extended.

1006
00:38:49,010 --> 00:38:49,780
According to the plan,

1007
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:51,400
once the development zone is established,

1008
00:38:51,760 --> 00:38:52,440
mining infrastructure projects

1009
00:38:52,740 --> 00:38:54,550
will be launched here first.

1010
00:38:54,960 --> 00:38:56,520
By then, manpower
and logistical support...

1011
