1013
00:38:59,500 --> 00:39:00,040
Get in the car!

1014
00:39:03,170 --> 00:39:03,670
Come on.

1015
00:39:03,690 --> 00:39:04,970
Everyone, hide behind the car.

1016
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:06,560
Go hide behind the car.

1017
00:39:06,590 --> 00:39:07,320
You two stay here.

1018
00:39:07,590 --> 00:39:07,880
Let's go. Let's go.

1019
00:39:07,900 --> 00:39:08,190
Let's go.

1020
00:39:08,500 --> 00:39:09,550
Hide behind the car.

1021
00:39:10,210 --> 00:39:10,650
Go! Go! Go!

1022
00:39:10,670 --> 00:39:11,460
Everyone hide behind the car.

1023
00:39:11,490 --> 00:39:12,370
Get behind the car. Quick.

1024
00:39:12,530 --> 00:39:13,530
Give me the gun. Quick.

1025
00:39:14,670 --> 00:39:15,400
Uncle Lin.

1026
00:39:16,700 --> 00:39:17,400
Protect them.

1027
00:39:18,510 --> 00:39:19,320
Stop the car!

1028
00:39:19,340 --> 00:39:20,160
Stop the car!

1029
00:39:20,420 --> 00:39:21,380
We are the Mountain Patrol.

1030
00:39:21,980 --> 00:39:23,120
Stop or we'll shoot!

1031
00:39:23,280 --> 00:39:23,880
Stop the car!

1032
00:39:24,380 --> 00:39:24,980
Stop!

1033
00:39:25,690 --> 00:39:26,520
Stop!

1034
00:39:26,780 --> 00:39:28,340
We are the Mountain Patrol!

1035
00:40:14,730 --> 00:40:15,420
Everyone get down!

1036
00:40:16,010 --> 00:40:16,360
Get down!

1037
00:40:16,380 --> 00:40:16,900
Make them get down!

1038
00:40:17,130 --> 00:40:17,460
Go.

1039
00:40:17,940 --> 00:40:18,270
Get down!

1040
00:40:18,690 --> 00:40:19,070
Get down!

1041
00:40:19,170 --> 00:40:20,130
Squat down. Come here.

1042
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:20,940
Get down!

1043
00:40:21,530 --> 00:40:22,030
Come here.

1044
00:40:22,150 --> 00:40:22,690
Hurry up.

1045
00:40:22,860 --> 00:40:23,550
Quick. Get down!

1046
00:40:26,510 --> 00:40:27,190
Where is that car?

1047
00:40:28,500 --> 00:40:29,420
