1051
00:40:36,520 --> 00:40:37,920
About fifty pieces.

1052
00:40:39,770 --> 00:40:40,750
This is normal.

1053
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:42,670
Zhacuo.

1054
00:40:42,970 --> 00:40:43,950
Did they hunt

1055
00:40:44,280 --> 00:40:45,230
