1060
00:40:51,380 --> 00:40:52,050
County Mayor Lin.

1061
00:40:52,380 --> 00:40:53,550
Oxygen. Get oxygen, quick.

1062
00:40:54,610 --> 00:40:55,230
What are you laughing at?

1063
00:40:55,250 --> 00:40:55,920
Get him to the car first.

1064
00:40:55,950 --> 00:40:57,030
Heads down. Don't move.

1065
00:40:57,050 --> 00:40:57,360
Sit back.

1066
00:40:57,380 --> 00:40:57,940
Officer.

1067
00:40:58,280 --> 00:40:59,150
Here.

1068
00:40:59,210 --> 00:41:00,290
