1069
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:00,860
Give it to him.

1070
00:41:00,960 --> 00:41:01,980
Take care of the rest of the people.

1071
00:41:02,010 --> 00:41:02,590
Don't worry. Don't worry.

1072
00:41:02,690 --> 00:41:03,260
Duojie,

1073
00:41:03,670 --> 00:41:04,900
I'm going to the County Hospital.

1074
00:41:04,900 --> 00:41:05,420
Take care of them.

1075
00:41:05,440 --> 00:41:06,210
Don't worry.

1076
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:06,900
I leave them to you.

1077
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:07,300
Don't worry.

1078
00:41:07,400 --> 00:41:08,360
Drive slowly, sir.

1079
00:41:10,010 --> 00:41:10,650
