1088
00:41:30,130 --> 00:41:31,860
It is the Mountain God's second wife.

1089
00:41:34,860 --> 00:41:36,220
The mountain to the north

1090
00:41:36,820 --> 00:41:37,660
is the Mountain God's

1091
00:41:37,680 --> 00:41:39,640
third son's wife.

1092
00:41:42,640 --> 00:41:43,440
The mountain to the south

1093
00:41:43,460 --> 00:41:44,910
is the Mountain God's steward.

1094
00:41:45,510 --> 00:41:46,250
What's wrong?

1095
00:41:46,570 --> 00:41:47,600
What did you say to him?

1096
00:41:48,670 --> 00:41:50,130
What did you say to him?

1097
00:41:50,420 --> 00:41:51,760
I was explaining the situation.

1098
00:41:52,950 --> 00:41:53,840
Duojie.

1099
00:41:54,420 --> 00:41:55,460
The site you chose today

1100
00:41:55,480 --> 00:41:56,430
was quite good.

1101
00:41:57,000 --> 00:41:58,290
To those who have never been here,

1102
00:41:58,320 --> 00:41:59,360
