1103
00:41:59,840 --> 00:42:01,530
We've seized the initiative.

1104
00:42:01,920 --> 00:42:02,900
You could say that.

1105
00:42:04,670 --> 00:42:05,520
Even though right now

1106
00:42:05,550 --> 00:42:06,880
