1111
00:42:14,840 --> 00:42:16,420
If you need money, just tell me.

1112
00:42:17,460 --> 00:42:18,550
Is 100,000 yuan enough?

1113
00:42:18,780 --> 00:42:19,330
No, no, no.

1114
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:20,090
Chairman Ding,

1115
00:42:20,640 --> 00:42:21,130
