1120
00:42:30,260 --> 00:42:30,900
didn't work out

1121
00:42:31,160 --> 00:42:32,600
and caused you

1122
00:42:32,680 --> 00:42:34,160
to lose a lot of money.

1123
00:42:35,050 --> 00:42:35,780
It wasn't your fault

1124
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:36,900
