1136
00:42:58,010 --> 00:42:59,020
Then, on behalf of the Mountain Patrol,

1137
00:42:59,050 --> 00:43:00,340
thank you, Chairman Ding.

1138
00:43:00,440 --> 00:43:01,540
We will definitely
get the exploration report done

1139
00:43:01,570 --> 00:43:02,420
